<BaseLayout title="How to Calculate a Discount: Sale Prices, Percentage Off, and Savings | ToolCalcs" description="Learn the discount formula, how stacking discounts works, how to add sales tax, and mental math shortcuts for common percentages off." structuredData={structuredData}>
